{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"2":{"eng-name":"Prayer (Kitab Al-Salat)","ara-name":"كتاب الصلاة"}},"section_detail":{"2":{"hadithnumber_first":391,"hadithnumber_last":1160,"arabicnumber_first":391,"arabicnumber_last":1160}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":933,"arabicnumber":933,"text":"Wail b, hujr said that he prayed behind the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ),and he said Amin loudly and saluted at his right and left sides until I saw the whiteness of his cheek","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":2,"hadith":544},"chapter":{"id":174,"ara-name":"باب التَّأْمِينِ وَرَاءَ الإِمَامِ","eng-name":"Saying 'Amin Behind The Imam","isFirstHadith":false}}]}